Any character can fall to their death. Characters (good + bad) can jump over holes; you can also push people around and push them off ledges (where they fall short distances and take a little damage, or fall far distances to their death). Falls within approx one average body height = no damage. Higher than that, but lower than 3.5 approx average body heights = take damage; ramp the damage by length of the fall. Higher than 3.5 = death from the fall
